OL,3,CCampaigners win their fight to reopen
OL,4,CCommunity Hospital
OL,6,FPeople in Bishop's Castle have been
OL,7,Fcelebrating after their campaign to
OL,8,Freopen the beds at their town's
OL,9,FCommunity Hospital succeeded.
OL,11,FThe Shropshire Community NHS Trust has
OL,12,Fagreed to reopen the 16 beds 'as soon
OL,13,Fas possible.'
OL,15,FThey closed in October 2021 because of
OL,16,Fstaffing problems. At that time there
OL,17,Fwas a 70% vacancy rate for registered
OL,18,Fnurses which the Trust said was unsafe
OL,19,Fand unsustainable.
